      "span_text": "Ifenprodil, a competitive antagonist at the stimulatory polyamine site has an overall negative modulatory effect on the receptor, decreasing the binding of MK-801 and its analogs.  Ifenprodil, at a relatively low dose, has a favorable anxiolytic-like profile without associated deficits in working memory in mice using the plus-maze paradigm."
